Class HDBOfficer

java.lang.Object
models.users.User
models.users.Applicant
models.users.HDBOfficer
public class HDBOfficer extends Applicant
Represents an HDB Officer in the BTO system. An HDB Officer is also an applicant and may be assigned to BTO projects.
